   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np"
   ],
   "id": "a4a6ae3948f5a537",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 5
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "# Часть 2: Получение переменных в реальных величинах / разностях / логарифмах и тд",
   "id": "b39da78bf44c05ed"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "### The aggregate U.S. real stock market return ( `ret_t` )\n",
    "\n",
    "Цитата из статьи:\n",
    "\n",
    "The aggregate U.S. real stock market return ( t ret )\n",
    "is obtained by subtracting the CPI inflation rate from the log returns on the CRSP valueweighted market portfolio\n",
    "\n",
    "Значит берем stock market return и делим на ИПЦ"
   ],
   "id": "71bfc71071461219"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "initial_id",
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": true,
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T14:49:19.830698Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T14:49:19.818940Z"
    }
   },
   "source": [
    "net_t = pd.read_csv(\"../original_data/processed/stock_market_return.csv\")\n",
    "net_t['date'] = pd.to_datetime(net_t['date'])"
   ],
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 2
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T14:50:55.262338Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T14:50:55.251441Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "cpi = pd.read_csv(\"../original_data/processed/cpi_us.csv\")\n",
    "cpi['date'] = pd.to_datetime(cpi['date'])"
   ],
   "id": "439f8f10062c3685",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 4
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T15:03:03.881179Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T15:03:03.875575Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "net_t = net_t.sort_values('date')\n",
    "cpi = cpi.sort_values('date')"
   ],
   "id": "92c628bcd4d94123",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 6
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T15:04:36.000946Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T15:04:35.997383Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "cpi['inflation'] = 100 * np.log(cpi['cpi_us'] / cpi['cpi_us'].shift(1))",
   "id": "981ed0bdd5763d69",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 9
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T15:05:07.987650Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T15:05:07.983121Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "ret_t = pd.merge(net_t, cpi[['date', 'inflation']], on='date', how='inner')",
   "id": "6a3d957bbe822863",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 11
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T15:07:01.014094Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T15:07:01.006960Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "ret_t['ret_t'] = ret_t['stock_market_return'] - ret_t['inflation']",
   "id": "d43bc29370806759",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 12
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T15:07:24.185108Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T15:07:24.182820Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "ret_t = ret_t[['date', 'ret_t']]",
   "id": "b83db2cfcac2361e",
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": 13
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-06-12T15:07:36.988129Z",
     "start_time": "2026-06-12T15:07:36.971277Z"
    }
   },
